methods.allowsReinterpret:
Test if a reinterpret call will succeed.

Note: Java generics information - <ALTERNATE_DATA_TYPE>

:param alternateDataType: (java.lang.Class<ALTERNATE_DATA_TYPE>) - The alternative type to consider

methods.isImmutable:
Determine if this column source is immutable, meaning that the values at a given index key never change.

:return: (boolean) true if the values at a given index of the column source never change, false otherwise
